---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { withBase } from '../utils/path';
---
<BaseLayout title="404 · Agent Pitfalls">
  <div class="py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-xl">
      <div class="code-block">
<pre class="m-0 border-0 p-0 font-mono text-[14px] leading-relaxed shadow-none" style="background: transparent;"><span class="tok-prompt">$</span> <span class="tok-cmd">curl</span> <span class="tok-key">-I</span> <span class="tok-string">{Astro.url.pathname}</span>
<span class="tok-comment">HTTP/1.1 404 Not Found</span>
<span class="tok-comment">x-powered-by: agent-pitfalls</span>
<span class="tok-comment">x-reason: 这一页的坑还没人踩过</span></pre>
      </div>

      <h1 class="mt-8 text-[32px] font-semibold leading-tight text-ink">404 · 这一页的坑还没人踩过</h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-slate">
        也许你想看的是避坑库、采集管线、或者直接到 GitHub 提交一个新坑。
      </p>

      <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-7 gap-y-3">
        <a href={withBase('/')} class="link-cta">回首页</a>
        <a href={withBase('/pitfalls')} class="link-cta">浏览避坑库</a>
        <a href={withBase('/contributing')} class="link-cta">提交新坑</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>